ml_tags: In Memory As part of us went with you For you didn't go alone It broke our hearts to lose you You were gone before we knew it No time to say goodbye No farewell words were spoken David (Dave) Matthews Mum, Dad, Bel, Justin, Marley, Taye & Loraine Love: And only God knows why The day God called you home. of 2nd Sept 73 - 31st July 21
